Class LinkedBinaryTree<E>

java.lang.Object
  binaryTree.LinkedBinaryTree<E>

BinarySearchTree
public class LinkedBinaryTree<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinaryTree<E>

The LinkedBinaryTree implements BinaryTree interface. When a LinkedBinaryTree is first created, it contains no items.

1.0
